  dnl
  dnl LT_INIT sets LIBTOOL, but we want this macro's setting of LIBTOOL to
  dnl persist.
  dnl Arghh: AC_BEFORE does not work in this setting :-(
  dnl AC_BEFORE([LT_INIT],[gl_RELOCATABLE_BODY])

